    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Korean BBQ Simulator</h2>Test your grilling skills in this fun and wacky - *cough* I mean, totally realistic physics-based meat grilling game based on Korean cuisine. This passion-project is a revival and re-envisioning of the classic Yakiniku and Meat Grilling games that were popular in Korea and Japan.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Different Modes for the Brave</h2>Challenge yourself with three different difficulties, three different modes, and a plethora of meats to cook.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137620/extras/menu.PNG?t=1689783422\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take Control and Turn Up the Heat</h2>Meats cook at different rates, be sure to adjust the grill's heat to match the type of meat you are cooking! <br>Eating raw or burnt meat can result in a penalty to your score and a stomach ache! Learn to master cooking multiple meats at the same time for maximum points!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137620/extras/Hanu_Grilling.PNG?t=1689783422\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become the Ultimate Korean BBQ Master</h2>Compete in online leaderboards against your friends, or even strangers around the world.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137620/extras/Score.PNG?t=1689783422\" /></span>",
